# Vendored IBM Plex assets are pinned byte-for-byte to upstream and SHA256-checked in
# tests/test_static_assets.py. Disable EOL normalization so the stored blobs stay identical
# to upstream regardless of a contributor's core.autocrlf setting (the upstream OFL.txt uses
# CRLF line endings; without this Git would smudge it to LF and break the pinned-hash test).
*.woff2 binary
OFL.txt -text
